07:07.723 --> 07:09.556
  Hey, that takes eight hours.

07:09.558 --> 07:11.592
  You know, I came for the pig,
 I stayed for the intervention.

07:11.594 --> 07:13.727
           I mean, no,
     I had to at that point.

07:13.729 --> 07:16.396
       I was, uh -- I was
   pig-committed, as they say.

07:16.398 --> 07:17.431
  What have you guys got here?

07:17.433 --> 07:18.432
             Bagels.
              Okay.

07:18.434 --> 07:19.800
          'Cause, yeah,

07:19.802 --> 07:21.235
     that's what New Orleans
          is known for.

07:21.237 --> 07:22.503
   Let me ask you a question.

07:22.505 --> 07:23.504
          How the hell
      did Raj make the cut?

07:23.506 --> 07:25.339
I love you, too, bro.

07:25.341 --> 07:28.342
Well, our biggest guest
hasn't even made it yet.

07:28.344 --> 07:30.110
            Oh, boy.
