              was a nightmare.

07:42.992 --> 07:45.092
Joe Buck is not here, Charlie.
You understand that?

07:45.094 --> 07:48.128
It's just his gigantic head
staring at me on the screen

07:48.130 --> 07:50.264
like the darkest version
     of "1984."

07:50.266 --> 07:54.301
        Hey, I'm calling
 a senior LPGA skins game today,

07:54.303 --> 07:57.371
