      Joe Buck in a second.

08:13.956 --> 08:15.455
             Just --
                 No, wait.
    I actually want to see this.

08:15.457 --> 08:17.858
               I got 200 bucks
              on Barb Moxness.

08:17.860 --> 08:19.026
    Come on, Jim.

08:19.028 --> 08:21.461
            Take this seriously!

08:21.463 --> 08:23.664
         We are all very worried
                 about you.

08:23.666 --> 08:27.534
So sit your ass down,
get ready to take
a goddamn moral inventory,

08:27.536 --> 08:29.503
   you ungrateful
   piece of shit.

08:29.505 --> 08:32.706
              Ooh.
You see why I can't stay, right?

08:32.707 --> 08:33.740
        Jim!

08:36.211 --> 08:38.278
      All I ask
is that you give this a try.

08:40.816 --> 08:42.182
             As a favor to you.

08:42.183 --> 08:43.683
